## 3. KEY FINDINGS
================================================================================

FINDING 1: DUAL AUTHENTICATION COMPLEXITY
The test suite confirmed the authentication divergence documented in phase3.report:
admin endpoints require API Key, store endpoints require JWT Bearer token.
Two separate test flows were required, consistent with hallazgo 5.3.1.

FINDING 2: SUITE GENERADA CON IA ES EXECUTABLE SIN MODIFICACION
The k6 scripts generated by the AI agent in Phase 4 were executable against
the FaaS endpoints with only environment configuration (URLs, credentials).
This validates the Phase 4 pipeline step as producing production-ready artifacts.

FINDING 3: COMPARISON SUITE READY
scripts/load-testing/comparison/faas-vs-iaas.js exists and is configured
for comparative benchmarking once both environments are deployed.
This is the key artifact for thesis sections 5.4, 5.5 and 5.6.

